ARM: stm32: debug: add low-level debug support

This adds low-level debug support on USART1 for STM32F4
and STM32F7.
Compiled via 'CONFIG_DEBUG_LL' and 'CONFIG_EARLY_PRINTK'.
Enabled via 'earlyprintk' in bootargs.

